<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us | MailMyWork.io</title>
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-95YQNPYWYM"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/google_analytics.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/main.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/navbar.css" />
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --accent-cyan: #00f0ff;
      --accent-blue: #1c55d0;
    }

    .about-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 80px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background: var(--glass);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .about-hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--accent-cyan) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-hero p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--accent-cyan);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-cyan), transparent);
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .info-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .info-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .info-card h3 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .info-card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .features-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .feature-label {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent-cyan);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .feature-value {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .wroomie-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 15px 35px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--accent-cyan));
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .wroomie-link:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      .about-container {
        margin: 40px 20px;
        padding: 25px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- SVG Gradient Definition for Logo -->
  <svg style="position: absolute; width: 0; height: 0;">
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="logoGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
        <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#1c55d0;stop-opacity:1" />
        <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#00f0ff;stop-opacity:1" />
      </linearGradient>
    </defs>
  </svg>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <header>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="logo">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z" fill="none"
            stroke="url(#logoGradient)" stroke-width="2" />
          <path d="M22 6l-10 7L2 6" fill="none" stroke="url(#logoGradient)" stroke-width="2" />
        </svg>
        MailMyWork.io
      </div>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/mail">Mail Me</a></li>
        <li><a href="/">Share Files</a></li>
        <li><a href="/feedback">Feedback</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="menu-toggle" id="menu-toggle">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="about-container">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Simplifying digital workflows and connecting people with their ideal living spaces.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Ecosystem</h2>
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>MailMyWork.io</h3>
          <p>MailMyWork is a cutting-edge productivity tool designed for the modern professional, developer, and student. It eliminates the friction of traditional communication by providing a lightning-fast, secure way to transfer snippets, files, and thoughts instantly.</p>
          
          <div class="features-list">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Instant Self-Mail</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Send notes to your inbox in seconds without logging in.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">PWA Ready</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Native OS share integration for a seamless mobile experience.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Secure Sharing</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Peer-to-peer file transfer with unique session codes.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Zero Friction</span>
              <span class="feature-value">No accounts, no ads, no trackers. Just pure utility.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card" id="wroomie-section">
          <h3>Wroomie.in (RoomieConnect)</h3>
          <p>Founded in 2026, <strong>Wroomie.in</strong> is a Mumbai-based platform that specializes in roommate matching and verified rental listings. It provides a user-friendly interface to search for rooms, PGs, and hostels using maps, filters, and verified listings to ensure a secure, brokerage-free experience.</p>
          
          <div class="features-list">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Target Audience</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Students & Professionals</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Verified Listings</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Focus on Trust & Safety</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Functionality</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Map-based Search & Matching</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <span class="feature-label">Company Info</span>
              <span class="feature-value">Mumbai, Maharashtra</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p style="margin-top: 20px;">The platform is designed to make finding a roommate and a new home a seamless, "stress-free" experience.</p>
          
          <a href="https://wroomie.in" target="_blank" class="wroomie-link">Visit Wroomie.in</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/navbar.js"></script>
  <script>
    gsap.from(".about-container", { opacity: 0, y: 30, duration: 1, ease: "power3.out" });
    gsap.from(".info-card", { 
      opacity: 0, 
      y: 20, 
      duration: 0.8, 
      stagger: 0.2, 
      ease: "power3.out",
      delay: 0.5 
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>
